Dialogue: 1,0:01:00.46,0:01:02.58,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,眠れない
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.58,0:01:05.25,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,お昼にコーヒー飲んだせいだ
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.84,0:01:07.59,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,やめなって言ったよ
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.17,0:01:11.13,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,だってかっこいいでしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.89,0:01:13.72,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,なに
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.52,0:01:28.99,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,あの人　うちでなにしてんの
Comment: 1,0:03:05.04,0:03:05.50,main-JP,,0,0,0,,main
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.50,0:03:07.13,main-JP,Iroha,0,0,0,,風ちゃんバイバイ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.13,0:03:08.67,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,また明日ね
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.37,0:03:11.67,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,あ〜眠い
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.34,0:03:14.80,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,昨日のあれ　何だったんだろう
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.38,0:03:16.88,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,あれってどれ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.88,0:03:18.72,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,うぐいすも見たでしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.72,0:03:21.39,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,庭でキラキラーって光ってて
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.39,0:03:22.77,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,キラキラ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.77,0:03:24.43,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,覚えてない
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.18,0:03:26.98,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,寝ぼけてたのかな
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.06,0:03:29.44,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ただいま
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.11,0:03:38.41,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,やっぱりいた
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.91,0:03:40.41,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,昨日の人
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.41,0:03:41.20,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,おや
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.66,0:03:45.29,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,ご機嫌よ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.29,0:03:47.42,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,君はここの家の人
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.42,0:03:49.25,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,そうですけど
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.25,0:03:52.50,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,あなたはうちの庭で何してるの
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.50,0:03:55.34,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,いい庭だったからお邪魔しているよ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.34,0:03:57.84,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,それはどうもってそうじゃなくて
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.84,0:03:59.51,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,勝手にダメだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.64,0:04:03.89,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,同胞の家かと思ってお邪魔したんだけど
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.89,0:04:06.10,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,君が人間みたいだね
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.10,0:04:09.48,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,でも　魔法の力を少し感じるな
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.48,0:04:10.81,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,えっ　ないよ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.81,0:04:13.15,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,魔法の力なんて全然ありません
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.15,0:04:15.03,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,心配しなくても
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.03,0:04:17.90,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,私はフェリックススターから来たんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.90,0:04:22.20,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,魔法の国の住人には知られても大丈夫だよ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.20,0:04:23.66,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,そうなんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.20,0:04:27.16,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,私野々山風　おじさんは
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.16,0:04:33.09,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,私の名前はピヨピヨン・ポンポローヌ・ニョロロンド・6世だ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.09,0:04:35.09,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,名前長いね
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.88,0:04:39.84,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,あのね　私も魔法の力をもらったんだけど
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.84,0:04:42.76,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,なんかうまくいかないんだよね
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.76,0:04:44.35,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,なんでだと思う
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.52,0:04:49.14,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,魔法と一言で言っても種類は様々
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.14,0:04:51.56,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,たとえはこうだ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.78,0:05:01.07,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,これくらいなら簡単かな
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.07,0:05:02.62,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,すごい
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.07,0:05:03.83,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,そうだ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.83,0:05:07.33,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,おじさん　私の魔法の先生になってよ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.33,0:05:08.54,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,先生
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.54,0:05:12.50,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,そう　もっと魔法がうまく使えるようになりたいの
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.58,0:05:16.05,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,ふん　でもどうかな
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.46,0:05:18.76,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,いいでしょ　お願いお願い
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.05,0:05:22.39,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,まあいいでしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.72,0:05:23.51,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ほんと
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.51,0:05:25.47,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,やったー
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.47,0:05:27.31,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,では行きましょうか
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.31,0:05:28.72,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,えっどこに
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.27,0:05:38.48,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,魔法について学ぶならここではダメだ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.48,0:05:41.07,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,魔法の国に行かないとね
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.07,0:05:42.49,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,えっ今から
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.82,0:05:46.12,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,でもあんまり遠くに行ったらダメだって
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.70,0:05:49.70,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,フェリックススターだ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.70,0:05:51.96,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,ようやった　帰れる帰れる
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.96,0:05:53.42,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,うぐいす
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.33,0:05:55.92,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ああ　待って
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.92,0:05:58.25,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,君も早く来なさい
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.72,0:06:02.01,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,もう
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.68,0:06:06.76,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,ただいま
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.77,0:06:11.14,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,急がないと
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.52,0:06:16.65,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,行ってきます
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.15,0:06:23.28,main-JP,Azuki,0,0,0,,これからなんのお仕事
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.70,0:06:27.20,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,事務所でオーディション用の動画を撮影するの
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.20,0:06:29.29,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,アテンションプリーズって
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.29,0:06:31.04,main-JP,Azuki,0,0,0,,かわいい
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.62,0:06:33.96,main-JP,Oleans,0,0,0,,あの
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.92,0:06:37.75,main-JP,Oleans,0,0,0,,ちょっといいですか
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.67,0:06:40.46,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,は　はい
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.46,0:06:42.76,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,この人怪しいかも
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.26,0:06:46.39,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,もしかして魔法の国の住人
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.60,0:06:49.26,main-JP,Oleans,0,0,0,,道を聞きたいんだけど
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.97,0:06:51.43,main-JP,Oleans,0,0,0,,喫茶ダブダブ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.43,0:06:53.27,main-JP,Oleans,0,0,0,,このカフェに行きたいんだけど
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.27,0:06:54.64,main-JP,Oleans,0,0,0,,どこだかわかる
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.02,0:06:57.15,main-JP,Oleans,0,0,0,,友人と待ち合わせしててね
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.15,0:06:59.57,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,事務所の隣のカフェ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.57,0:07:02.19,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,近くまで行くので案内します
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.19,0:07:04.32,main-JP,Oleans,0,0,0,,ほんと　助かるよ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.95,0:07:09.16,main-JP,Oleans,0,0,0,,この店パニーニがおいしいらしいんだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.16,0:07:10.70,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,そうなんですか
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.70,0:07:12.83,main-JP,Oleans,0,0,0,,チーズがとろっとしててね
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.29,0:07:15.04,main-JP,Oleans,0,0,0,,君はよく行くの
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.04,0:07:16.71,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,いえ　あまり
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.71,0:07:18.04,main-JP,Oleans,0,0,0,,へえ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.04,0:07:20.04,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,ここです
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.04,0:07:22.84,main-JP,Oleans,0,0,0,,まあ　ここだここ　ありがとう
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.84,0:07:25.09,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,じゃあ　私はこれで
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.09,0:07:25.97,main-JP,Oleans,0,0,0,,待って
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.51,0:07:28.30,main-JP,Oleans,0,0,0,,お礼にごちそうするよ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.93,0:07:31.43,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,大丈夫です　私急いでるから
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.76,0:07:33.72,main-JP,Oleans,0,0,0,,遠慮せずにさあさあ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.72,0:07:36.35,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,遠慮じゃないんです
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.94,0:07:45.95,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,ここが魔法の国
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.49,0:07:48.49,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,フェリックススターだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.95,0:07:51.91,main-JP,Magic Being (Cat),0,0,0,,なっとなに食べる
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.91,0:07:52.95,main-JP,Magic Being (Pig),0,0,0,,そうだな
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.75,0:08:00.29,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,なんだろう
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.29,0:08:02.71,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,なつかしい感じがする
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.17,0:08:06.17,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,空気うまーい
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.43,0:08:13.60,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,待て待て　魔法のレッスンをするんじゃなかったの
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.60,0:08:15.47,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,あっ　そうだった
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.02,0:08:17.89,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,さあ　始めよう
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.89,0:08:18.98,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.65,0:08:20.86,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,卵
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.86,0:08:23.48,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,魔法の練習用のたまごだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.48,0:08:26.15,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,初心者はまずこれを使う
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.15,0:08:27.36,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,へぇー
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.36,0:08:30.61,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,これを魔法で好きなものに変えてごらん
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.61,0:08:31.24,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.12,0:08:33.83,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,リリレラ　パリレラ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.83,0:08:37.00,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,卵よ　ケーキになーれ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.02,0:08:39.25,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,わくわく
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.05,0:08:47.67,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,失敗した
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.67,0:08:51.01,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,ふん　魔法の使い方がなってないなぁ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.39,0:08:55.77,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,これじゃ鰻を捕んでぬるりと逃げられたようなものだ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.14,0:08:57.27,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,そうなの
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.27,0:09:01.02,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,念じるときの心構えが大事なんだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.15,0:09:05.11,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,魔法を使うときは鰻じゃなくて
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.11,0:09:08.49,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,海老フライとかもっと大物を狙わないと
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.03,0:09:11.03,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.03,0:09:13.16,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,さあ　もう一度やってみなさい
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.66,0:09:16.41,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,リリレラ　パリレラ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.41,0:09:19.00,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,たまごよ　チョコレートになれ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.21,0:09:27.09,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,やったー　カバッピーだ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.09,0:09:28.34,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,チョコレートは
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.34,0:09:31.68,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,あっそっか　やっぱりうまくいかないなぁ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.09,0:09:36.18,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,ここだと　狭くてやる気が出ないのかもしれない
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.18,0:09:38.43,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,向こうにいい場所があるから
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.43,0:09:40.31,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,そこでやってみよう
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.31,0:09:43.19,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ねぇ　もっとわかりやすく教えてよ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.19,0:09:45.90,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,まあ　そんなに悪くないよ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.90,0:09:49.44,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,そもそも普通の人間は魔法が使えない
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.44,0:09:53.91,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,君の心に強い思いがあるから使えるんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.66,0:09:58.41,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,私の　強い思い
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.58,0:10:02.08,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,なんで　こんなことに
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.41,0:10:04.96,main-JP,Oleans,0,0,0,,へぇー　なかなかいい店だミイ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.96,0:10:07.21,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,私急いでるのに
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.38,0:10:10.01,main-JP,Meeter,0,0,0,,こんにちは
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.84,0:10:12.22,main-JP,Mari,0,0,0,,いらっしゃーい
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.55,0:10:15.80,main-JP,Oleans,0,0,0,,やぁ　久しぶりー
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.80,0:10:17.18,main-JP,Meeter,0,0,0,,失礼
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.56,0:10:19.93,main-JP,Meeter,0,0,0,,元気そうだねぇ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.56,0:10:21.73,main-JP,Azuki,0,0,0,,ミート
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.60,0:10:24.56,main-JP,Meeter,0,0,0,,おや　偶然だねぇ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.06,0:10:26.23,main-JP,Meeter,0,0,0,,ということは
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.57,0:10:28.98,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,ミートさん
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.98,0:10:31.40,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,初めましてルルです
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.40,0:10:33.78,main-JP,Meeter,0,0,0,,あずきから話は聞いているよ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.24,0:10:37.49,main-JP,Meeter,0,0,0,,この前の歌番組も良かったねぇ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.91,0:10:39.70,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.37,0:10:42.71,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,私　力をもらえて
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.83,0:10:46.79,main-JP,Oleans,0,0,0,,なんだ　二人は知り合いだったのか
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.26,0:10:53.51,main-JP,Azuki,0,0,0,,猫といえば私ミャオ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.01,0:10:55.38,main-JP,Mari,0,0,0,,ご注文は
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.38,0:10:58.18,main-JP,Meeter,0,0,0,,マジカルジュースとミックスフライジュース
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.18,0:10:59.89,main-JP,Meeter,0,0,0,,あと紅茶かな
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.89,0:11:02.35,main-JP,Oleans,0,0,0,,それとみんなにパニーニ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.73,0:11:04.27,main-JP,Mari,0,0,0,,はいはーい
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.27,0:11:06.52,main-JP,Mari,0,0,0,,紅茶はお砂糖3つね
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.61,0:11:10.36,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,あの　ミートさんは
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.82,0:11:13.53,main-JP,Meeter,0,0,0,,今日は彼と打ち合わせがあってね
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.53,0:11:17.36,main-JP,Meeter,0,0,0,,それで例の準備　どこまで進んでる
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.36,0:11:21.70,main-JP,Oleans,0,0,0,,うん　実行員が何人かに声はかけてるんだけど
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.70,0:11:24.87,main-JP,Oleans,0,0,0,,なかなかこれは　というのがいなくてね
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.37,0:11:27.63,main-JP,Meeter,0,0,0,,会場はどの辺になるんだい
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.63,0:11:30.46,main-JP,Oleans,0,0,0,,それもいくつか押さえてある
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.46,0:11:32.76,main-JP,Oleans,0,0,0,,君の意見も聞かせて欲しくてね
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.67,0:11:36.05,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,何の話
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.05,0:11:37.38,main-JP,Azuki,0,0,0,,分かんない
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.93,0:11:39.68,main-JP,Mari,0,0,0,,お待ちどうさまあ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.68,0:11:41.31,main-JP,Oleans,0,0,0,,お　来た来た
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.23,0:11:45.64,main-JP,Mari,0,0,0,,はい　紅茶
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.64,0:11:47.06,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 1,0:11:47.73,0:11:50.31,main-JP,Mari,0,0,0,,あんま変なのと付き合ったらダメだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.31,0:11:52.15,main-JP,Mari,0,0,0,,お姉さんは心配
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.11,0:11:56.40,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,いえ　私勝手に連れてこられて
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.40,0:11:56.82,main-JP,Oleans,0,0,0,,さあ　食べよ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.82,0:11:58.24,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,あの
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.82,0:11:58.24,main-JP,Meeter,0,0,0,,{\an8}これは美味いだ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.99,0:12:00.28,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,なーに ここ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.28,0:12:01.74,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,魔法の山だ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.20,0:12:05.25,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,練習するのにいい場所だと思ってね
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.41,0:12:10.13,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,この辺の人たちはよくここで山登りをするんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.13,0:12:12.38,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,周りにもっと高い山あるよ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.38,0:12:14.34,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,ここがいいんだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.67,0:12:17.93,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,登山口はこっちだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.97,0:12:20.18,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,こんにちは
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.18,0:12:21.72,main-JP,Magic Being (Gatekeeper),0,0,0,,子どもは入れないよ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.72,0:12:23.18,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,えぇ?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.18,0:12:26.73,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,そうか そうだった困ったな
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.73,0:12:29.27,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,大人なら入れるんだよね
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.90,0:12:31.94,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,リッと
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.90,0:12:34.40,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,リリレラ　パリレラ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.19,0:12:38.11,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,パムパムパワー
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.70,0:12:47.91,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,これでどう
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.91,0:12:50.12,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,これは驚いた
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.12,0:12:52.75,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,君　アイドルのリリィだったんだね
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.75,0:12:55.42,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,変身の魔法は完璧じゃないか
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.42,0:12:57.72,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,私のこと知ってるの
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.72,0:13:00.72,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,魔法のアイドルは珍しいからね
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.72,0:13:02.68,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,この国でも有名だよ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.68,0:13:04.68,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,そうなんだ　えへへ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.68,0:13:06.35,main-JP,Magic Being (Gatekeeper),0,0,0,,通っていいよ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.35,0:13:07.18,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.56,0:13:09.14,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,さあ　登ろう
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.14,0:13:09.69,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.15,0:13:16.53,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,着いたよ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.03,0:13:19.07,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,ここが頂上だ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.07,0:13:20.28,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,すぐだったね
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.28,0:13:21.66,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,疲れた
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.49,0:13:26.41,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,さて　早速練習だ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.41,0:13:28.91,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,次はどんな魔法がいいかな
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.75,0:13:33.83,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,この前　お姉ちゃんと喧嘩しちゃったの
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.83,0:13:36.92,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,そういう時にいい魔法ないかな
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.50,0:13:40.88,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,喧嘩した時はお互いに謝るのがいい
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.88,0:13:43.14,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,それが一番の魔法だよ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.76,0:13:46.10,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,先生みたい
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.43,0:13:47.77,main-JP,Magic Being (Pineapple),0,0,0,,あれ　リリィ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.77,0:13:49.85,main-JP,Magic Being (Tomato),0,0,0,,ほんとだ　アイドルのリリィだ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.02,0:13:52.85,main-JP,Magic Being (Wolf),0,0,0,,うわっすっげぇ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.85,0:13:54.40,main-JP,Magic Being (Pineapple),0,0,0,,テレビで見たよ!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.40,0:13:56.40,main-JP,Magic Being (Wolf),0,0,0,,なんで魔法の国にいるの
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.40,0:13:57.23,main-JP,Magic Being (Tomato),0,0,0,,歌って
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.23,0:13:58.82,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,いや　今はちょっと
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.82,0:14:02.78,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,あ君たち　リリィは魔法の練習があるんだから
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.78,0:14:03.74,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ごめんね
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.78,0:14:07.87,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,あリリィ　そっちに行ってはダメだ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.29,0:14:18.55,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,大丈夫か
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.37,0:14:22.84,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,あれ　どこ行ったんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.06,0:14:30.31,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,痛った
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.31,0:14:30.93,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,あれ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.06,0:14:34.94,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ここ　どこ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.61,0:14:37.90,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,うぐいす　起きて
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.23,0:14:40.40,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,にゃーに
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.82,0:14:43.99,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,転んだら変なところに落ちちゃったみたい
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.99,0:14:45.16,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,えぇ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.66,0:14:48.03,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,先生のとこ戻らないと
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.41,0:14:49.91,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,どうやって
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.29,0:14:52.29,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,わかんないけど
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.29,0:14:54.29,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,とにかく進んでみよう
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.29,0:15:00.42,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,ねぇ　怖い　帰ろうよ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.42,0:15:02.80,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,だから帰るんだって
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.42,0:15:05.68,main-JP,Oleans,0,0,0,,会場についてなんだけど
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.68,0:15:08.43,main-JP,Oleans,0,0,0,,鍾乳洞なんかどうかな
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.18,0:15:12.14,main-JP,Meeter,0,0,0,,高台のほうが良くない
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.14,0:15:14.14,main-JP,Oleans,0,0,0,,あそこは風が強いよ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.14,0:15:16.65,main-JP,Meeter,0,0,0,,でも洞窟は狭いだろう
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.65,0:15:18.23,main-JP,Oleans,0,0,0,,それもそうか
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.65,0:15:22.78,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,あの　私そろそろ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.78,0:15:25.40,main-JP,Oleans,0,0,0,,何か決め手はないかな
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.40,0:15:27.49,main-JP,Meeter,0,0,0,,それならいいものが
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.49,0:15:28.57,main-JP,Meeter,0,0,0,,店長
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.57,0:15:30.37,main-JP,Meeter,0,0,0,,地下に行ってもいい
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.37,0:15:32.83,main-JP,Mari,0,0,0,,え　いいけど
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.91,0:15:36.79,main-JP,Oleans,0,0,0,,君の意見も聞かせて欲しいねえ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.33,0:15:39.29,main-JP,Mari,0,0,0,,行っちゃって
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.63,0:15:41.88,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,あの　ごちそうさまでした
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.88,0:15:43.09,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,失礼します
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.09,0:15:44.59,main-JP,Oleans,0,0,0,,あっ、君!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.51,0:15:50.26,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,何だったんだろう　あの人たち
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.26,0:15:52.26,main-JP,Azuki,0,0,0,,お仕事お仕事
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.26,0:15:54.18,main-JP,Mari,0,0,0,,地下ね　テレビ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.18,0:15:54.93,main-JP,Meeter,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.69,0:16:04.74,main-JP,Oleans,0,0,0,,ええ　地下はこんな感じなんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.74,0:16:07.78,main-JP,Mari,0,0,0,,普段は常連しか入れないのよ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.58,0:16:12.53,main-JP,Mari,0,0,0,,つけるわよ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.37,0:16:18.37,main-JP,Oleans,0,0,0,,うん　良さそうじゃない
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.37,0:16:20.67,main-JP,Meeter,0,0,0,,高台も見てみようよ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.17,0:16:24.17,main-JP,Meeter,0,0,0,,やっぱりここがいいよ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.17,0:16:26.51,main-JP,Oleans,0,0,0,,いやいや　洞窟だよ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.18,0:16:34.35,main-JP,Mari,0,0,0,,嘘　リリィ　どうして
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.18,0:16:38.06,main-JP,Mari,0,0,0,,急用できたから　あなたたち店番してて
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.73,0:16:40.77,main-JP,Meeter/Oleans,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.15,0:16:45.15,main-JP,Mari,0,0,0,,リリィ　風
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.15,0:16:47.53,main-JP,Mari,0,0,0,,なんで魔法の国に
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.50,0:17:00.37,main-JP,Mari,0,0,0,,風　待ってて
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.29,0:17:06.38,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,誰かいませんか
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.01,0:17:09.63,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,おーい　誰か
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.39,0:17:13.55,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,なんで
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.01,0:17:16.64,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,さっきまでいっぱい人がいたのに
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.64,0:17:18.39,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,みんなどこ行っちゃったの
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.39,0:17:21.48,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,ねえ　もうおうち帰る
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.48,0:17:23.48,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,私だって帰りたいよ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.82,0:17:25.69,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,こっち
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.69,0:17:27.15,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,ほんと
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.21,0:17:46.96,main-JP,Mari,0,0,0,,まさかこっちに来ちゃうなんて
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.50,0:17:48.67,main-JP,Mari,0,0,0,,あの山は
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.13,0:17:51.68,main-JP,Mari,0,0,0,,人間が森の奥の聖地に入ったら
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.68,0:17:53.01,main-JP,Mari,0,0,0,,厄介なことになる
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.01,0:17:59.89,main-JP,Mari,0,0,0,,立ち入り禁止の看板　倒れてる
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.89,0:18:01.60,main-JP,Mari,0,0,0,,やっぱりこの中に
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.06,0:18:04.27,main-JP,Mari,0,0,0,,あの子を無事に連れて帰らないと
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.27,0:18:06.11,main-JP,Mari,0,0,0,,汐に怒られるよ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.24,0:18:15.20,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ねえ　ほんとにこっちかな
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.53,0:18:16.95,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,わかんない
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.95,0:18:20.70,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,魔法の世界ってもっと楽しいところじゃないの
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.70,0:18:22.83,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,楽しいな
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.64,0:18:42.27,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,誰かいませんかー
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.44,0:18:45.48,main-JP,Mari,0,0,0,,リリィこっち
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.90,0:18:49.36,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,誰もいない　やばーい
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.86,0:18:51.28,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,どうする
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.28,0:18:53.53,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,うぐいす　なんとかして
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.53,0:18:54.91,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,リリィがして!
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.53,0:18:57.32,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,あ　そうだ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.20,0:19:00.24,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,先生にもらった卵
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.62,0:19:02.29,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,リリレラ　パリレラ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.29,0:19:04.83,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,卵よ　森から連れ出して
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.92,0:19:11.34,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,あったかい
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.26,0:19:13.47,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,きれい
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.97,0:19:19.60,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,なんか元気出たかも　いこっかうぐいす
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.60,0:19:20.31,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.99,0:19:35.61,main-JP,Mari,0,0,0,,リリィ　何処
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.07,0:19:40.83,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,なんだろうあれ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.95,0:19:44.62,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,あそこは出口かも　行ってみよう
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.21,0:19:48.83,main-JP,Mari,0,0,0,,いた
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.46,0:19:53.00,main-JP,Mari,0,0,0,,ダメ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.03,0:20:17.03,main-JP,Mari,0,0,0,,間に合った
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.45,0:20:23.41,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,あれ　戻れた
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.41,0:20:24.49,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,よかった
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.49,0:20:26.75,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,おーい
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.75,0:20:29.88,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,こんなところにいたのか探してよ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.21,0:20:32.46,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,先生　どこ行ってたの
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.46,0:20:35.26,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,君の方こそどこに行ってたんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.21,0:20:38.76,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,魔法の練習はどうするかね
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.59,0:20:42.01,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,練習はもういいや
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.47,0:20:46.27,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,それに少しだけうまくできたんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.68,0:20:50.98,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,そうか　そりゃよかった
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.98,0:20:53.94,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,じゃあ　お家におかえり
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.15,0:21:00.11,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,さようなら　先生
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.49,0:21:03.95,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,もう知らない人の家の庭に入っちゃダメだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.95,0:21:04.83,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,ほう
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.33,0:21:06.29,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,じゃあね
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.29,0:21:07.58,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,やれやれ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.04,0:21:14.63,main-JP,Gentleman,0,0,0,,でもいい庭だったんだよなぁ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.09,0:21:20.30,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,アテンションプリーズ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.64,0:21:23.97,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,よし完璧
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.97,0:21:26.72,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,お疲れ様でーす
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.18,0:21:28.27,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,リリィ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.27,0:21:30.98,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,どうしたの　今日は仕事ないはずだけど
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.69,0:21:35.98,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,えへへ　なんだかみんなの顔が見たくなっちゃった
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.40,0:21:38.24,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,何かあったんですか
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.24,0:21:39.61,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,あった
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.61,0:21:42.07,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,すっごい色々あった
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.07,0:21:42.91,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,どうした
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.91,0:21:44.78,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,それは言えないんだけど
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.78,0:21:45.53,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.53,0:21:46.41,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,まあまあ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.41,0:21:47.91,main-JP,Azuki,0,0,0,,どうしたの
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.91,0:21:49.37,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,大変だった
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.37,0:21:50.71,main-JP,Azuki,0,0,0,,そう
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.79,0:21:53.63,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,でもちょうどよかった
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.63,0:21:56.21,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,リリィとルルに伝えたいことがあったんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.21,0:21:57.00,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,何
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.67,0:21:58.63,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,何ですか
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.63,0:22:01.47,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,実はねえ　なんとねえ
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.47,0:22:03.13,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,早く言ってあげな
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.43,0:22:07.39,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,実は今度　ライブをすることになりました
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.22,0:22:09.89,main-JP,Fuu/Rui,0,0,0,,ライブ
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.35,0:22:13.65,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,リリィとルル　二人のライブだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.52,0:22:16.06,main-JP,Fuu/Rui,0,0,0,,二人の
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.02,0:22:21.11,main-JP,Fuu/Rui,0,0,0,,ライブー
Comment: 0,0:00:38.06,0:00:41.06,main-CN,,0,0,0,,beforeop
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:43.40,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,今晚就决定在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.60,0:00:56.83,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,嗯 就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.46,0:01:02.58,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.58,0:01:05.25,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,都怪中午喝了咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.84,0:01:07.59,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,我都说了不让你喝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.17,0:01:11.13,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,因为很帅气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.89,0:01:13.72,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.52,0:01:28.99,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,那个人 在我们家做什么呢
Comment: 0,0:03:05.04,0:03:05.50,main-CN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.50,0:03:07.13,main-CN,Iroha,0,0,0,,小风拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.13,0:03:08.67,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.37,0:03:11.67,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,啊 好想睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.34,0:03:14.80,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,昨天的那个 到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:16.88,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,那个是哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:18.72,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,豌豆你不也看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.72,0:03:21.39,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,在庭院闪闪发光的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.39,0:03:22.77,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,闪闪发光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.77,0:03:24.43,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,你不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:26.98,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,是不是我睡迷糊了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:29.44,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:38.41,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,果然有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.91,0:03:40.41,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,昨天的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.41,0:03:41.20,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,哦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:45.29,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.29,0:03:47.42,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,你就是这家的主人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.42,0:03:49.25,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:52.50,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,你是谁 在我家的庭院里做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:55.34,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,因为庭院很棒 所以就来拜访一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.34,0:03:57.84,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,谢谢夸奖 诶 不对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.84,0:03:59.51,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,不要擅自进来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.64,0:04:03.89,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,我以为是同胞的家才来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.89,0:04:06.10,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,但你看起来是人类对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:09.48,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,但是 能些许感觉到魔法的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.48,0:04:10.81,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,诶 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:13.15,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,我根本没有魔法的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.15,0:04:15.03,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,不要担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.03,0:04:17.90,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,我是从幸运星来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:22.20,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,魔法之国的居民即使知道也没关系哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.20,0:04:23.66,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:27.16,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,我叫野野山风 大叔你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:33.09,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,我的名字是皮约皮约恩·蓬波罗奴·纽罗隆多六世
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.09,0:04:35.09,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,名字好长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.88,0:04:39.84,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,那个 我虽然获得了魔法的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:42.76,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,但是一直都使用不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:44.35,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,您认为是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.52,0:04:49.14,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,虽然魔法都被叫做魔法 但是种类繁多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:51.56,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,例如像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.78,0:05:01.07,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,这种魔法就比较简单吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:02.62,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:03.83,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,对啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.83,0:05:07.33,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,大叔 你能不能当我的魔法老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.33,0:05:08.54,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.54,0:05:12.50,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,是的 我想能更加熟练地使用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:16.05,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,嗯 但是这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:18.76,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,可以的吧 拜托了拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:22.39,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,那就依你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.72,0:05:23.51,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:25.47,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.47,0:05:27.31,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,那么我们出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.31,0:05:28.72,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,诶 去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:38.48,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,在这里可不能学习魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:41.07,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,必须要去魔法之国
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:42.49,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,诶 现在就去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:46.12,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,但是我不能去太远的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:49.70,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,是幸运星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:51.96,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,太好啦 回家啦回家啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.96,0:05:53.42,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,豌豆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:55.92,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,啊啊 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.92,0:05:58.25,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,你也快点进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.72,0:06:02.01,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,真的是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.68,0:06:06.76,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.77,0:06:11.14,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,要快点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:16.65,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,我出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:23.28,main-CN,Azuki,0,0,0,,接下来是什么工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.70,0:06:27.20,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,要在事务所拍试镜视频
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.20,0:06:29.29,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,「请注意」这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.29,0:06:31.04,main-CN,Azuki,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:33.96,main-CN,Oleans,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.92,0:06:37.75,main-CN,Oleans,0,0,0,,稍微打扰一下可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.67,0:06:40.46,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,嗯 您说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:42.76,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,这个人感觉好可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.26,0:06:46.39,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,难不成是魔法之国的居民
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.60,0:06:49.26,main-CN,Oleans,0,0,0,,我想问问路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:51.43,main-CN,Oleans,0,0,0,,胖胖咖啡店
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.43,0:06:53.27,main-CN,Oleans,0,0,0,,虽然我想要去这家店
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.27,0:06:54.64,main-CN,Oleans,0,0,0,,但你知道怎么过去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.02,0:06:57.15,main-CN,Oleans,0,0,0,,我和朋友约在那里见面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.15,0:06:59.57,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,是事务所旁边的咖啡店
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.57,0:07:02.19,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,刚好顺路 我带你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:04.32,main-CN,Oleans,0,0,0,,真的帮大忙啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.95,0:07:09.16,main-CN,Oleans,0,0,0,,这家店的帕尼尼听说非常好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.16,0:07:10.70,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:12.83,main-CN,Oleans,0,0,0,,芝士可是会融化的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.29,0:07:15.04,main-CN,Oleans,0,0,0,,你经常去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.04,0:07:16.71,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,啊 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.71,0:07:18.04,main-CN,Oleans,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:20.04,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,就这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:22.84,main-CN,Oleans,0,0,0,,啊 果然是在这 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.84,0:07:25.09,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,那么我 先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.09,0:07:25.97,main-CN,Oleans,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.51,0:07:28.30,main-CN,Oleans,0,0,0,,为表感谢 让我请你吃顿饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.93,0:07:31.43,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,没关系的 我赶时间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:33.72,main-CN,Oleans,0,0,0,,不用客气啦 快来快来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:36.35,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,我不是在客气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:45.95,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,这里就是魔法之国
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.49,0:07:48.49,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,幸运星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.95,0:07:51.91,main-CN,Magic Being (Cat),0,0,0,,等会吃什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.91,0:07:52.95,main-CN,Magic Being (Pig),0,0,0,,好问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.75,0:08:00.29,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:02.71,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,一种很怀念的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.17,0:08:06.17,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,空气好清新
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.43,0:08:13.60,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,等等 你不是要学习魔法课程吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.60,0:08:15.47,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,啊 对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.02,0:08:17.89,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,那么 我们开始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:18.98,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.65,0:08:20.86,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.86,0:08:23.48,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,这是练习魔法使用的蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:26.15,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,初学者就先用这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:27.36,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:30.61,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,试着用这个 通过魔法变成自己喜欢的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:31.24,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.12,0:08:33.83,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,莉莉露菈 啪礼露菈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.83,0:08:37.00,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,鸡蛋啊 变成蛋糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.02,0:08:39.25,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.05,0:08:47.67,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:51.01,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,嗯 你使用魔法的方法不正确
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.39,0:08:55.77,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,这简直就是竹篮打水一场空
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.14,0:08:57.27,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.27,0:09:01.02,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,祈愿时候的心态可是非常重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.15,0:09:05.11,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,使用魔法的时候不要只盯着鳗鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.11,0:09:08.49,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,而是盯着像是炸大虾等更有价值的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.03,0:09:11.03,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.03,0:09:13.16,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,好了 再来一次试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.66,0:09:16.41,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,莉莉露菈 啪礼露菈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.41,0:09:19.00,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,鸡蛋啊 变成巧克力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.21,0:09:27.09,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,好耶 是卡八匹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.09,0:09:28.34,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,巧克力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.34,0:09:31.68,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,啊 对哦 果然还是不顺利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:36.18,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,可能是这里太过狭窄提不起精神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:38.43,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,那边有个好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:40.31,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,去那边试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.31,0:09:43.19,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,呐 再更加浅显易懂一点呗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.19,0:09:45.90,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,嘛 这也不算很难理解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.90,0:09:49.44,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,再说了 普通人类本就无法使用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:53.91,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,因为你内心拥有强烈的心意才能使用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.66,0:09:58.41,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,我的 强烈心意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.58,0:10:02.08,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,为什么 变成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:04.96,main-CN,Oleans,0,0,0,,诶 感觉这家店还不错呢咪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:07.21,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,我明明赶时间来着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.38,0:10:10.01,main-CN,Meeter,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.84,0:10:12.22,main-CN,Mari,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:15.80,main-CN,Oleans,0,0,0,,哟 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:17.18,main-CN,Meeter,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.56,0:10:19.93,main-CN,Meeter,0,0,0,,看起来你最近挺不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.56,0:10:21.73,main-CN,Azuki,0,0,0,,米特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:24.56,main-CN,Meeter,0,0,0,,哦呀 好巧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.06,0:10:26.23,main-CN,Meeter,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.57,0:10:28.98,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,米特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:31.40,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,初次见面 我叫露露
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:33.78,main-CN,Meeter,0,0,0,,我从红豆那里听说了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.24,0:10:37.49,main-CN,Meeter,0,0,0,,之前的音乐节目很不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.91,0:10:39.70,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.37,0:10:42.71,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,我 获得了力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:46.79,main-CN,Oleans,0,0,0,,什么啊 两位是熟人呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.26,0:10:53.51,main-CN,Azuki,0,0,0,,说起猫的话我才是喵～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.01,0:10:55.38,main-CN,Mari,0,0,0,,您要点些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:58.18,main-CN,Meeter,0,0,0,,魔法果汁和混合油炸果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.18,0:10:59.89,main-CN,Meeter,0,0,0,,再来一杯红茶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.89,0:11:02.35,main-CN,Oleans,0,0,0,,然后再给各位都来一份帕尼尼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.73,0:11:04.27,main-CN,Mari,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.27,0:11:06.52,main-CN,Mari,0,0,0,,红茶放三勺砂糖对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.61,0:11:10.36,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,那个 米特是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.82,0:11:13.53,main-CN,Meeter,0,0,0,,今天和他来这里开会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.53,0:11:17.36,main-CN,Meeter,0,0,0,,然后 那件事准备工作进行到哪一步了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:21.70,main-CN,Oleans,0,0,0,,嗯 虽然我找了好几个执行委员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:24.87,main-CN,Oleans,0,0,0,,但没一个让人眼前一亮的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:27.63,main-CN,Meeter,0,0,0,,会场选在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.63,0:11:30.46,main-CN,Oleans,0,0,0,,这个我也提前准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:32.76,main-CN,Oleans,0,0,0,,但还是想听听你的建议
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:36.05,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,他们在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.05,0:11:37.38,main-CN,Azuki,0,0,0,,不造
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.93,0:11:39.68,main-CN,Mari,0,0,0,,各位久等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.68,0:11:41.31,main-CN,Oleans,0,0,0,,哦 来啦来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.23,0:11:45.64,main-CN,Mari,0,0,0,,来 红茶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:47.06,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.73,0:11:50.31,main-CN,Mari,0,0,0,,可别跟些奇奇怪怪的人交往哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:52.15,main-CN,Mari,0,0,0,,姐姐我很担心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.11,0:11:56.40,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,不是 我是被迫带进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:11:56.82,main-CN,Oleans,0,0,0,,好 来吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:11:58.24,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:11:58.24,main-CN,Meeter,0,0,0,,{\an8}这个很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.99,0:12:00.28,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,这里是哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:01.74,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,魔法之山
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:05.25,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,我认为是练习魔法的好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:10.13,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,附近的人经常来这里登山
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.13,0:12:12.38,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,旁边还有更高的山哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.38,0:12:14.34,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,这边更好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.67,0:12:17.93,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,登山口在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.97,0:12:20.18,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.18,0:12:21.72,main-CN,Magic Being (Gatekeeper),0,0,0,,小孩子不能进去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:23.18,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:26.73,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,这样啊 这可麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.73,0:12:29.27,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,只要是「大人」就能进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.90,0:12:31.94,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.90,0:12:34.40,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,莉莉露菈 啪礼露菈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:38.11,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,帕姆帕姆力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:47.91,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,这样如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.91,0:12:50.12,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,这可真是大吃一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.12,0:12:52.75,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,你竟然是偶像莉莉呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:55.42,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,变身魔法很完美呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:57.72,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,你知道我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.72,0:13:00.72,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,魔法偶像可是很少见的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.72,0:13:02.68,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,所以你在这个国家很有名
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.68,0:13:04.68,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,这样啊 嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:06.35,main-CN,Magic Being (Gatekeeper),0,0,0,,可以进去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.35,0:13:07.18,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.56,0:13:09.14,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,好了 登山吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:09.69,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.15,0:13:16.53,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.03,0:13:19.07,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,这里就是山顶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.07,0:13:20.28,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.28,0:13:21.66,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:26.41,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,那么 我们赶紧练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:28.91,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,接下来想要学什么魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:33.83,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,前几天 我和姐姐吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.83,0:13:36.92,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,这种时候用什么魔法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:40.88,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,吵架的时候只要互相道歉就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:43.14,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,这可是最有效的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.76,0:13:46.10,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,好像老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.43,0:13:47.77,main-CN,Magic Being (Pineapple),0,0,0,,啊嘞 莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.77,0:13:49.85,main-CN,Magic Being (Tomato),0,0,0,,真的啊 是偶像莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.02,0:13:52.85,main-CN,Magic Being (Wolf),0,0,0,,哇 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:54.40,main-CN,Magic Being (Pineapple),0,0,0,,我在电视里看过你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.40,0:13:56.40,main-CN,Magic Being (Wolf),0,0,0,,为什么来到魔法之国呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.40,0:13:57.23,main-CN,Magic Being (Tomato),0,0,0,,唱歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:13:58.82,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,不行 现在稍微有点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.82,0:14:02.78,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,你们几个 莉莉还要练习魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:03.74,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:07.87,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,啊 莉莉 不能去那边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:18.55,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.37,0:14:22.84,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,啊嘞 她去哪里了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.06,0:14:30.31,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.31,0:14:30.93,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,啊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:34.94,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,这里 是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.61,0:14:37.90,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,豌豆 快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:40.40,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,咋了喵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.82,0:14:43.99,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,摔了一跤后 好像掉进什么奇怪的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.99,0:14:45.16,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.66,0:14:48.03,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,必须要回到老师那边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.41,0:14:49.91,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,怎么回去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.29,0:14:52.29,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.29,0:14:54.29,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,总之先往前走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:15:00.42,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,呐 好恐怖 快点回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:02.80,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,都说了正在回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:05.68,main-CN,Oleans,0,0,0,,关于会场的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.68,0:15:08.43,main-CN,Oleans,0,0,0,,钟乳洞怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:12.14,main-CN,Meeter,0,0,0,,高台更好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:14.14,main-CN,Oleans,0,0,0,,但高台风太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:16.65,main-CN,Meeter,0,0,0,,但是洞穴很狭窄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.65,0:15:18.23,main-CN,Oleans,0,0,0,,这倒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.65,0:15:22.78,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,那个 我是时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.78,0:15:25.40,main-CN,Oleans,0,0,0,,有没有关键的决定因素呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:27.49,main-CN,Meeter,0,0,0,,要这么说有个好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.49,0:15:28.57,main-CN,Meeter,0,0,0,,店长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:30.37,main-CN,Meeter,0,0,0,,可以去地下室吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.37,0:15:32.83,main-CN,Mari,0,0,0,,诶 可以是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:36.79,main-CN,Oleans,0,0,0,,我们也想听听你的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:39.29,main-CN,Mari,0,0,0,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.63,0:15:41.88,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,那个 感谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:43.09,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.09,0:15:44.59,main-CN,Oleans,0,0,0,,那个 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.51,0:15:50.26,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,到底怎么回事呢 他们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:52.26,main-CN,Azuki,0,0,0,,工作工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:54.18,main-CN,Mari,0,0,0,,地下室对吧 看电视吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:54.93,main-CN,Meeter,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:04.74,main-CN,Oleans,0,0,0,,诶 地下室竟然是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.74,0:16:07.78,main-CN,Mari,0,0,0,,平时只有熟客才能进来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.58,0:16:12.53,main-CN,Mari,0,0,0,,要开电视咯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:18.37,main-CN,Oleans,0,0,0,,嗯 感觉很不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:20.67,main-CN,Meeter,0,0,0,,也看看高台吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.17,0:16:24.17,main-CN,Meeter,0,0,0,,果然这里更好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:26.51,main-CN,Oleans,0,0,0,,不不 洞穴更好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.18,0:16:34.35,main-CN,Mari,0,0,0,,不是 莉莉 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:38.06,main-CN,Mari,0,0,0,,我突然有急事要处理 你们帮我看下店
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.73,0:16:40.77,main-CN,Meeter/Oleans,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.15,0:16:45.15,main-CN,Mari,0,0,0,,莉莉 风
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.15,0:16:47.53,main-CN,Mari,0,0,0,,为什么在魔法之国
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.50,0:17:00.37,main-CN,Mari,0,0,0,,风 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.29,0:17:06.38,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,有人在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.01,0:17:09.63,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,喂 有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.39,0:17:13.55,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:16.64,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,明明刚刚还有很多人在的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:18.39,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,大家都去哪里了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.39,0:17:21.48,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,呐 赶紧回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.48,0:17:23.48,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,我也想回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.82,0:17:25.69,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,走这边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.69,0:17:27.15,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:46.96,main-CN,Mari,0,0,0,,没想到她竟然来到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:48.67,main-CN,Mari,0,0,0,,那座山是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:51.68,main-CN,Mari,0,0,0,,如果人类进入了森林深处的圣地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.68,0:17:53.01,main-CN,Mari,0,0,0,,会惹上大麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:17:59.89,main-CN,Mari,0,0,0,,禁止进入的标志倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.89,0:18:01.60,main-CN,Mari,0,0,0,,果然她就在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.06,0:18:04.27,main-CN,Mari,0,0,0,,要是不把她平安带回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:06.11,main-CN,Mari,0,0,0,,小汐会生气的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.24,0:18:15.20,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,说起来 真的是这边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:16.95,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,我不造
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.95,0:18:20.70,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,魔法的世界不应该是更为快乐的存在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:22.83,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,快是快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.64,0:18:42.27,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,有人在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.44,0:18:45.48,main-CN,Mari,0,0,0,,莉莉 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.90,0:18:49.36,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,谁也不在 惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.86,0:18:51.28,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.28,0:18:53.53,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,豌豆 你快想想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.53,0:18:54.91,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,莉莉你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:18:57.32,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:19:00.24,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,老师给我的蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.62,0:19:02.29,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,莉莉露菈 啪礼露菈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.29,0:19:04.83,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,鸡蛋哟 带我们出森林吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.92,0:19:11.34,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,好温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.26,0:19:13.47,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.97,0:19:19.60,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,感觉有点精神了 我们走吧豌豆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.60,0:19:20.31,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.99,0:19:35.61,main-CN,Mari,0,0,0,,莉莉 在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:40.83,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,那个 是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:44.62,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,那边可能是出口 走去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.21,0:19:48.83,main-CN,Mari,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:53.00,main-CN,Mari,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.03,0:20:17.03,main-CN,Mari,0,0,0,,赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:23.41,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,啊嘞 回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.41,0:20:24.49,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.49,0:20:26.75,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.75,0:20:29.88,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,你们在这里啊 我好找呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.21,0:20:32.46,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,老师 你去哪里了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:35.26,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,我还想问你们去哪里了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.21,0:20:38.76,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,魔法的练习该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.59,0:20:42.01,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,练习就算啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.47,0:20:46.27,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,而且我感觉 稍微做得好一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.68,0:20:50.98,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,这样啊 那真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.98,0:20:53.94,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,那么 我送你回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.15,0:21:00.11,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,老师再见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.49,0:21:03.95,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,不要再到陌生人家的庭院里了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.95,0:21:04.83,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.33,0:21:06.29,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.29,0:21:07.58,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,诶呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:14.63,main-CN,Gentleman,0,0,0,,但是那个庭院真的很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.09,0:21:20.30,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,请注意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.64,0:21:23.97,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,好 完美
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.97,0:21:26.72,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:28.27,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.27,0:21:30.98,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,怎么了呢 今天你应该没有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.69,0:21:35.98,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,诶嘿嘿 总想来见见大家这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.40,0:21:38.24,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,发生了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.24,0:21:39.61,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:42.07,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,超多事情发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:42.91,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,比如说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.91,0:21:44.78,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,不过那些都不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.78,0:21:45.53,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.53,0:21:46.41,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,算了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.41,0:21:47.91,main-CN,Azuki,0,0,0,,怎么了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.91,0:21:49.37,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.37,0:21:50.71,main-CN,Azuki,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.79,0:21:53.63,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,但是正好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.63,0:21:56.21,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,有件事情要告诉你们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.21,0:21:57.00,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.67,0:21:58.63,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,会是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.63,0:22:01.47,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,实际上 竟然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.47,0:22:03.13,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,快点告诉她们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.43,0:22:07.39,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,实际上我们 决定近期开演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.22,0:22:09.89,main-CN,Fuu/Rui,0,0,0,,演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.35,0:22:13.65,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,莉莉和露露 你们两人的演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.52,0:22:16.06,main-CN,Fuu/Rui,0,0,0,,两人的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.02,0:22:21.11,main-CN,Fuu/Rui,0,0,0,,演唱会
